{
  "chapter": 63,
  "chapter_summary": "武当大殿灯火辉煌，木道人率道众入殿，各路武林豪杰齐聚。陆小凤藏身横梁，暗中监视伪装混入的敌人。武当掌门石雁戴着紫金道冠主持继承人仪式，内心疲倦紧张。仪式进行中，七十二盏长明灯突然全灭，黑暗中惨呼连连。灯亮后，铁肩、王十袋、巴山小顾等多位高手倒在血泊中。石雁的紫金道冠被盗，七星剑被拔出。木道人镇定主持大局，带精英弟子追凶。身份神秘的高大威猛老人与石雁交谈后也前往追击。群豪议论纷纷，无人知晓老人真实身份。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁有火折子？快燃灯。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 146
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "凶手一定还在这里，真相未明之前，大家最好全都留下来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "无论谁只要走出这大殿一步，都不能洗脱凶手的嫌疑，那就休怪本门子弟，要对贵客无礼了。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "凶手绝不止一个人，他们一击得手，很可能已乘着刚才黑暗时全身而退了，但却不可能已全都退出武当。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "既然大家都得留在大殿里，谁去追他们？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "木道人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "我去。我还得带几个得力的人去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": "char_mu_dao_ren",
      "text": "本门弟子，但凭师叔调派。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_da_wei_meng_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高大威猛的老人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "果然如此。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事变非常，只得委屈各位在此少候，无垢先带领本门弟子，将死难的前辈们抬到听竹院去，无镜、无色带领弟子去巡视各地，只要发现一件兵刃，就快报上来。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_da_wei_meng_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高大威猛的老人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "你最好让他们先搜搜我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 195,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": "char_gao_da_wei_meng_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "你若要杀人，又何必用刀剑？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_da_wei_meng_de_lao_ren",
      "speaker_name": "高大威猛的老人",
      "listener": "char_shi_yan",
      "text": "那么我也想陪你师叔去追凶。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 197,
      "line_end": 197
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shi_yan",
      "speaker_name": "石雁",
      "listener": "char_gao_da_wei_meng_de_lao_ren",
      "text": "请。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "群豪甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们不能走，他为什么能走？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao_yi",
      "speaker_name": "群豪乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "因为他的身份和别人不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 201,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao_jia",
      "speaker_name": "群豪甲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qun_hao_yi",
      "speaker_name": "群豪乙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他就是那……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 63,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    }
  ],
